<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-become-aware-of">be / become aware of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>对……知道、明白；意识到……</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People around the world should be aware of the real situation of water shortage.
全世界人民都应该意识到水资源短缺的真实情况。</p><footer>2010 福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They suddenly became aware of people looking at them.
他们突然发觉有人在看着他们。</p></div></div>